ivals :
  nlayer : contains the @number of layers (2 or 3) in the sample
  lams   : array containing thermal conductivities of the layer @nlayer (in @kg s^-3 m K^-1).
  kappas : contains radius of
      - sample (in @mm)
      - laser (in @mm)
      - measuring (in @mm)
  Rs: Heat transfer coefficient for losses in  @kg s^-3 m K^-1
      - from front face
      - from rear face
      - curved side face
  tflash : duration of laser flash in @ms
